2) cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a novel model for similarity measurement between child-parent pairs. 
3) cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper discusses the impact of understanding kin relationships on the behavior of AI agents in the human world. 
4) cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image-based kinship verification. 
5) cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper discusses feature selection methods for kinship verification.
